係拉到人頭都好, 都唔夠還財仔啲息。<br />\n<br />\n所謂同你嘅&quot;好朋友&quot;合作做生意, 唔好用情感行事, 一定要理性, 畢究錢係你出。<br />\n<br />\n利申: 中過招, 期望唔好有其他人中<br />\n最後, 我鍾意咗番工<br />\n無一個行業係仆街得過佢"},{"pid":"f291cb8565d6a835352e1a31df5c5c91894e408a","tid":2494082,"uid":364562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e06877f69fd4c58b9aac62277fe808e7d98f3f1b","tid":2494082,"uid":52509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"45332633aa633fa6b25edc4b0b4ef7cad95c651b","tid":2494082,"uid":366105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aa5b4037c29d9b3580d824d03e643fa37c27ee56","tid":2494082,"uid":364562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:44:18.000Z","msg":"先貼上個Post先<br />\n<br />\n入黎分享各行各業嘅黑暗面<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2489326\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2489326</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n以為audit 黑暗，原來仲有好多行業<br />\n睇到泯滅人性，好興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想再聽多啲，請大家踴躍分享"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:58:36.000Z","msg":"啲科學園r funding 公司係咪開兩三年就執<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T23:48:18.000Z","msg":"兩三年就踢你走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T02:09:10.000Z","msg":"換個負責人再玩有冇得諗？"},{"pid":"84d292e79834e3fd895b6c98ee6e5df53ff1e203","tid":2494082,"uid":140664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T02:30:21.000Z","msg":"Mphil phd 老細會想有個人留左幾年幫手執頭執尾而格硬唔比你畢業"},{"pid":"2ec0d06f05c825036bada169d6826c94324d5df7","tid":2494082,"uid":395282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8344d75ceb45d7135a5310bbee9073df9a4f0478","tid":2494082,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T07:37:03.000Z","msg":"X芳奶茶 條布抹完雪櫃再抹杯邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8fecd6f805fead87ca1858e330bf5405347e51a